Jenkins is used for running the tests, reporting errors, and creating new stable releases.

The following Jenkins plugins should be installed:
	
Hudson CMake plugin	
Measurement Plots
Hudson Performance Publisher plugin
Hudson Post build task
Publish Over SSH
Python Plugin
Hudson SSH Slaves plugin
Hudson Subversion Plug-in
Subversion Release Manager plugin
Hudson Subversion Tagging Plugin
Hudson Edgewall Trac plugin
Jenkins xUnit plugin
Downstream buildview plugin
Global Build Stats Plugin
Dependency Graph View Plugin
